QuestData.Title: Tree Delivery
QuestData.Description: Here you go, one instant Super-Gro Insta-Tree made with 80% natural ingredients!$B$BNo roots, no muss, no fuss. Just give it to Kilram and make sure he stands the heck back when he uses it.
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the Super-Gro Insta-Tree to Kilram at the inn in Everlook.
QuestData.RewardText: Alright! Stand back now and watch what a true quality weapon can do!
